---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NavSimple from '../components/NavSimple.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - Burst2GIF by boost.photo" description="Privacy Policy for Burst2GIF Lightroom plugin by boost.photo." noindex={true}>
  <div class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-50 min-h-screen">
    <NavSimple dark={true} />

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <main class="py-20 lg:py-28">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-12">Last updated: January 2025</p>

            <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Burst2GIF is a desktop plugin that runs entirely on your computer.
                        We don't collect, store, or transmit your photos or personal data.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What we collect</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-400">
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">Email address:</strong> Only if you download the free version or make a purchase.
                            Used solely to deliver your download link and important product updates.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">Payment information:</strong> Processed securely by LemonSqueezy.
                            We never see or store your credit card details.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What we don't collect</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li>&bull; Your photos (they never leave your computer)</li>
                        <li>&bull; Personal information beyond email</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Cookies and tracking</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        This website uses the following technologies that may collect data:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-400">
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">Google Analytics:</strong> We use Google Analytics to understand
                            how visitors interact with our website. This service collects information such as your IP address
                            (anonymized), browser type, pages visited, time spent on pages, and referral sources.
                            This data helps us improve our website and marketing. Google Analytics uses cookies to collect
                            this information. You can opt out by declining cookies when prompted or by using the
                            <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">Google Fonts:</strong> We use Google Fonts to display the Inter font.
                            When you visit our website, your browser downloads fonts from Google's servers, which involves
                            the transmission of your IP address to Google.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
                        Google may use this information in accordance with their privacy policy:
                        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">policies.google.com/privacy</a>
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Third-party services</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-400">
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">LemonSqueezy:</strong> Handles payments and email delivery.
                            See their privacy policy: <a href="https://www.lemonsqueezy.com/privacy" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lemonsqueezy.com/privacy</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-slate-300">Vercel:</strong> Hosts this website. Vercel may collect
                            standard server logs (IP address, browser type, access times) for security and performance purposes.
                            See their privacy policy: <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Data retention</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Your email address is retained for as long as necessary to provide you with product updates
                        and support. If you wish to have your email removed from our records, please contact us
                        and we will delete it within 30 days.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Legal basis for processing (GDPR)</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        We process your personal data based on the following legal grounds:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Contract performance:</strong> Processing your email to deliver the purchased product.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Legitimate interest:</strong> Sending important product updates and security notices.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Consent:</strong> Using Google Analytics to analyze website traffic (you can withdraw consent at any time by clearing cookies or using browser settings).</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">International data transfers</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Some of our third-party service providers (Google, Vercel, LemonSqueezy) are based in the United States.
                        When your data is transferred outside the European Economic Area, these providers ensure appropriate
                        safeguards are in place, such as Standard Contractual Clauses approved by the European Commission,
                        to protect your personal data in accordance with GDPR requirements.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Your rights (GDPR)</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        If you are located in the European Economic Area, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right of access:</strong> You can request a copy of your personal data.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to rectification:</strong> You can request correction of inaccurate data.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to erasure:</strong> You can request deletion of your personal data.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to restrict processing:</strong> You can request limitation of processing in certain circumstances.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to data portability:</strong> You can request your data in a machine-readable format.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to object:</strong> You can object to processing based on legitimate interest.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to withdraw consent:</strong> Where processing is based on consent, you can withdraw it at any time.</li>
                        <li>&bull; <strong class="text-slate-300">Right to lodge a complaint:</strong> You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. In the Czech Republic, this is the Office for Personal Data Protection (UOOU) at <a href="https://www.uoou.cz" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition" target="_blank" rel="noopener">uoou.cz</a>.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mt-4">
                        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at the email address below. We will respond within 30 days.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-400">
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Name:</strong> Marek Topolar</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Business ID (IC):</strong> 04923804</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Address:</strong> Borkovany 310, 691 75 Borkovany, Czech Republic</li>
                        <li><strong class="text-slate-300">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@boost.photo" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300 transition">hello@boost.photo</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </section>
            </div>

            <p class="mt-16 text-sm text-slate-500">
                &copy; 2025 Marek Topolar | IC: 04923804 | Borkovany 310, 691 75 Borkovany
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
